Package: genoPlotR
Type: Package
Title: Plot Publication-Grade Gene and Genome Maps
Version: 2.0.0
Date: 2024-05-16
Author: Lionel Guy <lionel.guy@imbim.uu.se>,  Mike V. Puijk <mikepuijk@hotmail.com>
Depends:
    grid
Imports: 
    ade4,
    ape,
    data.table,
    gtools,
    methods,
    stats,
    utils
Suggests:
    knitr,
    optparse,
    rmarkdown
Maintainer: Mike V. Puijk <mikepuijk@hotmail.com>
Description: Draws gene or genome maps and comparisons between these, in a 
   publication-grade manner. Starting from simple, common files, it will 
   draw postscript or PDF files that can be sent as such to journals.
